      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "UNKNOWN LIMITS (2) last start finished 4th in a Mix 5 on July 10 over 390m at Q Lakeside behind Into Oblivion beaten 9 lengths (22.76). Suited here and can find winning form. SHE'S BUBBLES (4) boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten 2 lengths (16.75) behind Noaki Warrior at this track. Expected to feature. NON STOP TOMMY (1) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing sixth (30.19) in a OPEN at Rockhampton. Goes very well here finding the frame in each of five starts. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Cannot be taken lightly. GOLDEN EYE (6) gets a chance to improve on an unplaced run at her latest outing at this circuit.",
